        	<span class="readonly"><h1>Highlighter GK4<small>ver. 1.5</small></h1><p>GK4 is new generation of our extensions dedicated to Joomla! 1.6.</p><p>Highlighter GK4 is news rotator which allows to present chosen articles headers in an attractive way. Thanks to multiple options, users may adjust it to their needs. Additionally, Highlighter GK4 can be integrated with any source of information.</p> <p class='homepage'><a href='http://tools.gavick.com/highlighter.html' target='_blank'>Learn more at the Highlighter GK4 project website.</a></p><p class='license'>Weather GK4 is released under the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html">GNU/GPL v2 license.</a></p></span>

        ]]></description>

		

